        i.material-icons 
      .user-activity__item__content
        span.text-light 2 Days ago
        p
          | Marked
          a href="#"  3 tasks
          | as
          span.badge.badge-pill.badge-outline-danger Invalid
          | inside the
          a href="#"  Shards Dashboards
          | project.
